front.title: •Head Back To The Surface
front.gametext: If your piloted unique (•) starfighter is present with opponent's piloted starfighter during your move phase at a non-cloud sector, relocate both to related system. OR Target your starfighter in battle. During this battle, your other starships may not be targeted by weapons.
front.lore: 'And see if you can get a few of those TIE fighters to follow you.'
